Party Scroller:
Displays text messages sent to a Google Voice number on a web page

Requirements:
	sqlite
	Gmail http://mail.google.com
	Google Voice http://www.google.com/voice
	
Setup:
	bundle install
	create gmail account
	setup google voice with text forwarding to gmail
	edit 'confg.yml'
	
Run:
	ruby party-scroller.rb
	ruby gmail-script.rb
	
	load http://localhost:4567/ in your web browser